Package abyss.plugin.api.entities

Class PathingEntity

java.lang.Object
abyss.plugin.api.entities.Entity
abyss.plugin.api.entities.PathingEntity
All Implemented Interfaces:
Identifiable, Locatable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Npc, Player
public abstract class PathingEntity extends Entity implements Identifiable
A snapshot of a pathing entity (character) in the game world. This data is constant, and will not be changed after this object is created.
